<li>Bitcoin offers a&nbsp;modern alternative to traditional methods&nbsp;of international money transfers, providing&nbsp;fast and cost-effective solutions</li>



<li>Cryptocurrency transactions offer benefits such as&nbsp;lower transaction fees,&nbsp;faster processing times,&nbsp;enhanced security and&nbsp;greater accessibility</li>



<li>When sending Bitcoin internationally, users need to be aware of risks such as&nbsp;volatility,&nbsp;security vulnerabilities or the&nbsp;lack of widespread acceptance</li>
